rows.label: tev999926_SEL0031
rows.name: This BLADE operative is standing by for orders.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999926_MSG0101
rows.name: There you are! I've been waiting for you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999926_MSG2001
rows.name: I've relayed your request for division support![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999926_MSG2102
rows.name:
I was hoping you'd ask me to come along.
It's sooooo boooooring here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999926_MSG2103
rows.name:
But of course, your request for division support will
be granted. You don't need to worry about that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999926_MSG3001
rows.name:
Clearly you have a keen eye for talent.
Together, we will be unstoppable![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999926_MSG3102
rows.name:
Finally, an opportunity to show you how crazy tough
I can be when the poop hits the fan![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999926_MSG5001
rows.name:
I'm in the middle of a top-secret assignment right now!
So don't talk to me, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999926_MSG5101
rows.name:
I know it doesn't look like it, but I'm in the middle of
something right now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999926_MSG5102
rows.name:
It's, like, meditation...or something? And I'm not
supposed to be interrupted. But I'll have attained
enlightenment soon, so let's talk then.[ST:wait ]
